name: Camino Tumbado
description:
This song was created in the summer of 2020, in this song I talk about my lifestyle and how calm I like to live it, I also talk about how we must always be careful of those who do not want to see us well and only hinder the way with negativity and bad vibes. The cover art of this song is very special because for this time I had a different mask that will not come out again. All the production of this song and the visuals were created by me (Blu).

Artist- Sad Blu 
Producer- Sad Blu 
Cover Art- Sad Blu
